STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Jose D. LOPEZ-DURANGO, a/k/a Jose D. Durango, Lose D. Durango, and Jose D. Lopez, Defendant-Petitioner. 082008
C-841 September Term 2018 Supreme Court of New Jersey. May 3, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004252-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
